comments: LeVert (CLE) does not establish a legal guarding position prior to contact taking place with Powell (LAC) as Powell moves to LeVert's side at the end of the drive.
Mann (LAC) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before elevating for the shot attempt.
Mann's (LAC) left hand brushes the netting and he does not grab it or cause the rim to vibrate unnaturally during the dunk attempt.
Morris Sr. (LAC) and Mobley (CLE) engage and disengage with one another near the wing.
After initially engaging and disengaging with one another, Powell (LAC) moves forward slightly and marginal body contact occurs with LeVert (CLE) near the top of the perimeter.
Jackson (LAC) initiates contact with Garland's (CLE) left arm, affecting Garland's SQBR and causing him to lose control of the ball.
Garland (CLE) grabs and pulls Jackson's (LAC) jersey away from his body, causing him to become dislodged as he pursues the loose ball.

Jackson (LAC) brushes Garland's (CLE) side and marginal body contact occurs at the end of Garland's drive. George (LAC) then brings his hand toward Garland's path and marginal contact occurs with Garland's front as he elevates to pass.
George (LAC) jumps from point A to point B and delivers body contact to Allen (CLE) that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Mitchell (CLE) swipes forward with his right hand and initiates contact with Powell's (LAC) left arm after his gather.
George (LAC) brings his hands toward Allen's (CLE) right side and marginal contact occurs as Allen moves to set the pick.
Jackson (LAC) briefly has his arm around Allen's (CLE) midsection during the box-out and quickly disengages as the long rebound falls toward the corner.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Garland (CLE) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Jackson (LAC) re-establishes slightly in Okoro's (CLE) path following the initial contact during the screen and further marginal contact occurs as Okoro moves around it.
Okoro (CLE) extends forward and initiates body contact with George (LAC) during the driving shot attempt.
LeVert (CLE) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Mann (LAC) engages and disengages with Mitchell (CLE) during the inbound.
George (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Mitchell (CLE) prior to incidental contact occurring.
Morris Sr. (LAC) engages and disengages with Mobley (CLE) along the perimeter.
Garland (CLE) is moving alongside Jackson's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs as the play moves in transition.
Garland (CLE) trails Jackson (LAC) from behind and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Jackson's front.
Garland (CLE) is moving forward slightly when marginal body contact occurs with Jackson (LAC) near the top of the perimeter.
Garland (CLE) brushes Jackson's (LAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Jackson makes the pass.
Mobley (CLE) moves forward into Morris Sr. (LAC) and initiates contact with Morris Sr.'s front after he receives the pass. The contact occurs prior to a potential traveling violation.
Jackson (LAC) delivers body contact to Garland (CLE) near half-court.
Wade (CLE) immediately slides his hand off of Jackson's (LAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Jackson cuts during the inbound.
Wade (CLE) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
George (LAC) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Zubac (LAC) engages and disengages with Allen (CLE) during rebounding.
Mitchell (CLE) commits a take foul on George (LAC).
George (LAC) and Powell (LAC) each jump to the side of Love (CLE) and marginal body contact occurs as Love starts his dribble.
George (LAC) avoids making contact with Love (CLE) as Love starts his upward shooting motion.
